description:
Timeless, unisex and simply adorable this is a super cute drawstring pant option for your newborn, changing your little one has never been so simple! GOTS certified 100% certified organic cotton.
Fabric & Fit : Soft | Lightweight | Functional | Fabulous Printing: Water based non toxic inks. Soft and really long lasting.
WASH & CARE , Save the Climate. Wash cool - Line dry. Handwash at 30 C inside out. Wash with similar colors. Do not soak or bleach. Reshape while damp. Iron inside out at a low temperature. Do not iron decoration.
name: DUSG Classic drawstring pants
short_description: DUSG Classic drawstring pants in organic Cotton
